Package: ggguides
Title: Simplified Legend and Guide Alignment for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gilles", "Colling", email = "gilles.colling051@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides one-liner functions for common legend and guide operations in 'ggplot2'. Simplifies left-aligned legends, wrapped legend layouts, and legend collection across multi-panel plots created with 'patchwork' or 'cowplot'.
